.TH "mipi_dsi_create_packet" 9 "mipi_dsi_create_packet" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mipi_dsi_create_packet \- create a packet from a message according to the DSI protocol
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" mipi_dsi_create_packet
.BI "(struct mipi_dsi_packet *packet "  ","
.BI "const struct mipi_dsi_msg *msg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "packet" 12
pointer to a DSI packet structure
.IP "msg" 12
message to translate into a packet
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or a negative error code on failure.
